---
title: Pork and Peppers in Peanut Sauce with Carrots and Coconut Rice
description: It may sound a little strange, but trust us, peanut butter is the secret to making this dish shine in unexpected ways. Paired with coconut rice, this recipe is comforting and satisfying beyond comprehension!
